race.description: Become A Brc Member Qtis 3yo Handicap (Bm65)
race.comment: WHISPERING ROGUE (2) peaks for the in-form Munce yard and was close up twice at Eagle Farm before being cruelled by a wide gate at Ipswich, beaten 2L. Enjoys this track and distance and presents on an 8-day return. Ready to win. HUNTER'S MATE (3) spaced the Maidens at Ipswich first-up and then was on-speed again beaten a short half head at this track in a 68. She was heavily bet and today she's advantaged by the inside gate. Third-up and should get all the favours. ENFORCEABLE (6) was beaten a half length in the same contest and is also a winning chance. Hard fit and he always puts in. OZZIE INVADER (8) will build on the narrow Maiden win at the Sunshine Coast.
